OL,3,CInquiry: Prosecuting criminals with
OL,4,Cmental illness should be 'default'
OL,6,FA psychiatry expert has told the
OL,7,FNottingham attacks Inquiry that
OL,8,Fpursuing criminal charges against
OL,9,Fpeople with a mental illness, should
OL,10,Fbe the "default approach".
OL,12,FParanoid schizophrenic Valdo Calocane
OL,13,Fkilled students Barnaby Webber and
OL,14,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and
OL,15,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, 65, in the early
OL,16,Fhours of June 13 2023, before trying
OL,17,Fto kill three others with a van.
OL,26,@rD@HOUrD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
