OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776791154
OL,3,CInquiry: Prosecuting criminals with
OL,4,Cmental illness should be 'default'
OL,6,FThe former mechanical engineering
OL,7,Fstudent was not charged by police over
OL,8,Fa series of violent offences before he
OL,9,Fcarried out the stabbings.
OL,11,FSeena Fazel, Professor of Forensic
OL,12,FPsychiatry, told the central London
OL,13,Finquiry that prosecuting someone
OL,14,Fenables an "accurate picture of their
OL,15,Frisks" in the future.
OL,26,@vD@LOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776791154
OL,3,CInquiry: Prosecuting criminals with
OL,4,Cmental illness should be 'default'
OL,6,FHe said: "When serious interpersonal
OL,7,Fviolence has come to the attention of
OL,8,Fthe police or the clinical team,
OL,9,Fpursuing criminal charges should be
OL,10,Fconsidered a default approach, rather
OL,11,Fthan dropping charges.
OL,13,F"For many reasons ` one of them is
OL,14,Fthat the very act of pursuing criminal
OL,15,Fcharges is quite important as a signal
OL,16,Fto the individual that their actions
OL,17,Fhave consequences and these people are
OL,18,Ftaking it seriously.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776791154
OL,3,CInquiry: Prosecuting criminals with
OL,4,Cmental illness should be 'default'
OL,6,F"The second reason is that pursuing
OL,7,Fcriminal charges is quite important in
OL,8,Fterms of record keeping as well.
OL,10,F"Sometimes what happens, particularly
OL,11,Fif people move services, is that's the
OL,12,Fonly way you'll know someone has a
OL,13,Fhistory of any violence ` they may not
OL,14,Ftell you about it."
OL,16,FCalocane was arrested in May 2020 when
OL,17,Fhe repeatedly kicked at a woman's door
OL,18,Funtil she jumped out of the first-
OL,19,Ffloor window from fear, causing damage
OL,20,Fto her spine which required surgery.
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
