CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776791154
OL,3,CInquiry: Prosecuting criminals with
OL,4,Cmental illness should be 'default'
OL,6,FSurvivors of the Nottingham attacks
OL,7,Fhave told an official inquiry that
OL,8,Fpolice failures caused "extra
OL,9,Fsuffering" for victims' families
OL,11,FA forensic psychiatrist who
OL,12,Frecommended that triple killer Valdo
OL,13,FCalocane be given a hospital order,
OL,14,Fdid not view footage of previous
OL,15,Fincidents he had been involved in
OL,16,Fbefore writing his report.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776791154
OL,3,CInquiry: Prosecuting criminals with
OL,4,Cmental illness should be 'default'
OL,6,FOn another occasion before the fatal
OL,7,Fattacks, Calocane held his flatmate in
OL,8,Fa headlock and pushed another student
OL,9,Fagainst a wall before trying to get
OL,10,Finto his bedroom in the middle of the
OL,11,Fnight and following him home.
OL,13,FThe killer was not prosecuted over
OL,14,Fthese incidents.
OL,16,FCalocane was charged with assaulting
OL,17,Fan emergency worker after he
OL,18,Fheadbutted, punched and swung
OL,19,Fhandcuffs at a Nottinghamshire Police
OL,20,Fofficer who was trying to detain him
OL,21,Funder mental health laws in 2021.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776791154
OL,3,CInquiry: Prosecuting criminals with
OL,4,Cmental illness should be 'default'
OL,6,FBut he was not arrested for months
OL,7,Fafter failing to attend court and was
OL,8,Fthe subject of a warrant when he
OL,9,Fcarried out the fatal attacks.
OL,11,FJust weeks before the killings, he
OL,12,Fassaulted two people at a factory but
OL,13,Fpolice body-worn footage connected to
OL,14,Fthis was mistakenly deleted.
OL,16,FCalocane had been diagnosed with
OL,17,Fparanoid schizophrenia in 2020 and was
OL,18,Fdetained under mental health laws four
OL,19,Ftimes, before he was handed an
OL,20,Findefinite hospital order for
OL,21,Fmanslaughter and attempted murder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
