OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1776791154
OL,3,CInquiry: Prosecuting criminals with
OL,4,Cmental illness should be 'default'
OL,6,FProf Fazel said it has been "very
OL,7,Fdifficult" to link health and crime
OL,8,Frecords in the UK, saying "There are
OL,9,Fvarious issues, a lot to do with
OL,10,Fconfidentiality and concerns around
OL,11,Fidentifying people and also working
OL,12,Facross health and justice systems".
OL,14,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
